data.description: Discover the perfect blend of style and comfort in this 4-bed, 2-bath home. The fourth bedroom, nestled on the second story, offers flexibility as a game room or guest suite. The split master arrangement boasts a double sink vanity, relaxing garden tub, and a roomy walk-in closet. This home's design shines with a seamless flow from the formal dining area into the open living space, making it ideal for entertaining. The spacious kitchen is a culinary delight, complete with a breakfast room and convenient bar seating. Step out onto the covered patio, adorned with a charming pergola, and experience outdoor living at its finest. The fenced backyard offers privacy and a safe space for pets or children to play. Plus, you'll appreciate the convenience of a two-car garage for parking and storage. This home presents a unique opportunity to create your dream lifestyle. Don't miss out on making it your own!
